snippet.title: Azoove Steam Next Fest Demo Premiere Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2435450/Azoove/

Adventure with friends in this co-op card roguelike, bravely crossing the dangerous Azoove desert. Manage resources and communicate effectively to survive the journey and return the cursed book to the Library. Can you make it in time to seal the evil fiend Ur'gan?
